description: Moving forward to a new chapter in life, I'm letting go of my most prized possession. Lucid Lu, I never painted the name on but I named her for the manifestation of a lifelong dream. Turn and go. Purrs like a kitten. Relatively new upholstery, and a Bumping stereo system. Cozy front cabin for overnighters. Jam from the harbor to the islands in an hour flat on a calm day. In the two years that I've owned her I've: been on half a dozen islands trips, had the engine cleaned and serviced, re-painted the trailer and replaced the trailer jack, replaced the batteries, made a whole lot of memories. She's looking for a new home; a fellow dreamer and nautical adventurer. What works: engine, stereo, radio, most of the electronics, everything important. What doesn't work: a few of the gauges on the dash. That's about it to my knowledge. Fully equipped to coast guard standards. What's included: 2 anchors, life jackets, bumpers and plenty of line, mobile charger/battery jumper, wakeboard (if you want it), Hawaiin sling (if you want it), fish finder (not sure if it works, I never used it), token hula girl, whatever else I forgot to mention.... description: Moving forward to a new chapter in life, I'm letting go of my most prized possession. Lucid Lu, I never painted the name on but I named her for the manifestation of a lifelong dream. Turn and go. Purrs like a kitten. Relatively new upholstery, and a Bumping stereo system. Cozy front cabin for overnighters. Jam from the harbor to the islands in an hour flat on a calm day. In the two years that I've owned her I've: been on half a dozen islands trips, had the engine cleaned and serviced, re-painted the trailer and replaced the trailer jack, replaced the batteries, made a whole lot of memories. She's looking for a new home; a fellow dreamer and nautical adventurer. What works: engine, stereo, radio, most of the electronics, everything important. What doesn't work: a few of the gauges on the dash. That's about it to my knowledge. Fully equipped to coast guard standards. What's included: 2 anchors, life jackets, bumpers and plenty of line, mobile charger/battery jumper, wakeboard (if you want it), Hawaiin sling (if you want it), fish finder (not sure if it works, I never used it), token hula girl, engine oils and gas additives, ..... Come take a test drive. I'm moving to the bay in less than 5 weeks so I'm hoping to sell it soon and I will be accepting offers.
